GPT-Chat is an open-source chatbot framework that uses natural language processing and machine learning to enable developers to create custom chatbots. It is based on OpenAIs GPT-2 model, a natural language processing model that has been trained on large datasets of text. GPT-Chat enables developers to quickly build and deploy custom chatbots that can understand conversational language and respond in a natural way. GPT-Chat also supports integration with external services such as Facebook Messenger, Slack, and Telegram.